          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI916FDusle2dbUqPKbYAEjJTtysvgvQYsgrXX9Ci04OdUHMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "I was so scared to go to a female doctor. Rosa from the appointment office gave me a good doctor. Rosa also was kind and patience with me over the phone. She explained a lot of things to me. I got to meet her today.  Dr. Holtzman is such a good and nice doctor! Her assistant Angelique is very nice too, they both made you feel comfortable. The whole office is nice over there and I didn't wait long for nothing. The best part is everything is right there! All of them need a bonus and raise! I love to go to a place, where I feel comfortable and this is it! Also, I went to do a MRI there and Shonda and Ray was very nice to me. I'm so comfortable around them to the point for me it went fast.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21jMVUxRXdNMDloTTBRNVowbERVV0pvYmxsdUxYYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xd9eefc10e462be80!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmc1U1EwM09hM0Q5Z0lDUWJoblluLXc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "Edited 4 months ago",
