          "description": "Very beautiful facility, amazing staff. Special thanks to laboratory nurses. Wanderful people in chemotherapy department. Registration is fast and efficient. Passing messages to doctors and responses very accurate. And of course Dr. Paula Klein, nurse Nancy Rocklain, Emma. They are the best. Always listen to the patients needs. And all the attending personnel. Happy New Year.",
