          "description": "I had an excellent experience at this facility under the care of Dr. Rosen. The hospital staff was attentive, professional, and made me feel at ease throughout the process. My procedure was efficient, and I was in and out within a few hours. While I can\u2019t speak for the other doctors, I can confidently say that Dr. Rosen is an exceptional gynecologist. Her expertise, compassionate care, and clear communication truly stood out. I highly recommend her to anyone in need of a skilled and caring GYN specialist.",
