          "description": "Had a second bone marrow biopsy. Jill Wickham who performed procedure was extremely professional prior to procedure. Dr. Patel was anesthesiologist who was very calming before and after procedure. No pain and no memory of any of the procedure. This biopsy procedure should never be performed without sedation. I highly recommend this facility.",
