          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI1N088kI7_-oYt5kK0zwxQwhAC_G_wQP90Bd14cU8WvGelKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Highly recommend switching to NYU or Lenox Hill for anything related to radiology or breast care. I switched and have had a much better experience! It\u2019s impossible to reach anyone by phone (or messaging on their portal for that matter) at Mount Sinai; they often don\u2019t have appointments for months; the people working there are often unfriendly and impatient; and they bill you from a billion different departments so that the cost of care is exorbitant even with insurance. I\u2019ve loved my experiences both with NYU and Lenox Hill. Everyone I interact with is kind and caring, and it\u2019s easy to call and get an appointment! HUGE difference from Mount Sinai :)",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aT1lrUnlaMFJ1Y3pOSGJrdDRVako0Y0c1bWRIYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xd9eefc10e462be80!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOnZOYkRyZ0RuczNHbkt4UjJ4cG5mdHc%7C%7C?hl=en",
